  "summary": {
    "as": "Passed House",
    "asOf": "2022-09-30",
    "date": "2023-08-14T16:38:55Z",
    "text": "Fairness for 9/11 Families Act\n\nThis bill authorizes and provides funding for lump-sum catch-up payments from the United States Victims of State Sponsored Terrorism Fund to 9/11 victims, 9/11 spouses, and 9/11 dependents.\n\nThe bill also rescinds specified unobligated funds that were provided to the Small Business Administration for the Paycheck Protection Program."
